<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 03:12:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>华北客车撞隧道墙 14人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/passenger-bus-crashes-into-tunnel-wall-north-china-killing-14-2024-03-20/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周三报道，周二，中国北方山西省一辆客车撞上隧道墙，造成 14 人死亡、37 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 03:06:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/passenger-bus-crashes-into-tunnel-wall-north-china-killing-14-2024-03-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行改组货币政策委员会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-reshuffles-monetary-policy-committee-2024-03-20/</link><description>中国央行表示，已对货币政策委员会进行改组，其中包括证监会主席吴清、央行副行长宣长能和两名新的学术委员。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 03:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-reshuffles-monetary-policy-committee-2024-03-20/</guid></item><item><title>台湾警告其南中国海附近有“巨大”的中国基地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-warns-enormous-chinese-bases-near-its-schina-sea-holding-2024-03-20/</link><description>台湾外交部长周三表示，中国已在台湾在南海主要领土周围的三个岛屿上建立了“巨大”的军事基地，但台北并不打算进一步加剧战略航道的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 02:46:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-warns-enormous-chinese-bases-near-its-schina-sea-holding-2024-03-20/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟、联合国批评香港新国安法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/european-union-un-criticise-new-hong-kong-security-law-2024-03-20/</link><description>欧盟和联合国表示，香港的新国家安全法案令人深感担忧，可能会侵蚀这座中国统治城市的基本自由。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 02:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/european-union-un-criticise-new-hong-kong-security-law-2024-03-20/</guid></item><item><title>美联储会议前亚洲股市震荡，日元跌至4个月低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-20/</link><description>周三，亚洲股市犹豫不决，原因是担心美联储可能暗示今年降息步伐将放缓，而日元则因预期日本政策将在更长时间内保持宽松而跌至四个月新低。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 02:15:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-20/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉将从4月1日起提高中国生产的Model Y汽车的价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-raise-price-china-produced-model-y-vehicles-april-1-2024-03-20/</link><description>周三，特斯拉向路透社证实，该公司将从 4 月 1 日起将中国生产的 Model Y 车辆的价格提高 5000 元人民币（694.55 美元）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 02:06:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-raise-price-china-produced-model-y-vehicles-april-1-2024-03-20/</guid></item><item><title>日元徘徊在四个月低点附近，美联储成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-flounders-near-four-month-low-fed-spotlight-2024-03-20/</link><description>周三，在日本央行决定结束负利率政策的第二天，日元兑美元汇率跌至近四个月低点，兑欧元汇率跌至 16 年来的低点。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 01:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-flounders-near-four-month-low-fed-spotlight-2024-03-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国维持基准贷款利率不变，符合预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-leaves-benchmark-lending-rates-unchanged-expected-march-2024-03-20/</link><description>在整体经济出现一些改善迹象的情况下，央行上周维持关键政策利率不变，周三中国将基准贷款利率维持在月度固定利率不变，符合市场预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 01:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-leaves-benchmark-lending-rates-unchanged-expected-march-2024-03-20/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟在华企业“过度”偏重风险管理——商业集团</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-firms-china-skewed-disproportionately-towards-risk-management-business-group-2024-03-20/</link><description>欧洲商业游说团体周三警告称，在华欧洲企业过于注重风险管理，而不是增加市场份额，这损害了效率和创新，并增加了消费者的成本。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 01:09:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-firms-china-skewed-disproportionately-towards-risk-management-business-group-2024-03-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国外长称中澳经济“高度互补”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-foreign-minister-says-china-australia-economies-highly-complementary-2024-03-20/</link><description>根据中国外交部周三发布的声明，中国外交部长王毅在与澳大利亚外长会晤时表示，中国和澳大利亚经济“高度互补”，潜力巨大。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 00:18:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-foreign-minister-says-china-australia-economies-highly-complementary-2024-03-20/</guid></item><item><title>Nvidia 年度开发者大会的要点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/key-takeaways-nvidias-annual-developer-conference-2024-03-19/</link><description>英伟达在本周的年度开发者大会上推出了其下一代大型人工智能芯片以及多个合作伙伴和软件工具，寻求在推动人工智能热潮的竞争中保持领先地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 23:00:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/key-takeaways-nvidias-annual-developer-conference-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯普京表示新任期首访将考虑中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russias-putin-says-he-will-consider-china-his-first-trip-new-term-2024-03-19/</link><description>俄罗斯总统普京周二晚间表示，他将考虑在周末选举中获得的新总统任期内首次出访中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 22:45:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russias-putin-says-he-will-consider-china-his-first-trip-new-term-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>外长会晤后澳大利亚准备迎接中国总理访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-top-diplomat-meets-australian-counterpart-canberra-2024-03-19/</link><description>澳大利亚外交部长黄英贤在堪培拉与中国外长王毅举行会谈后表示，澳大利亚和中国将为今年中国总理李强的访问做准备，澳大利亚称会谈内容涵盖人权、关税和地区安全。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 22:40:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-top-diplomat-meets-australian-counterpart-canberra-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国检察官称，中国加拿大人窃取了特斯拉机密</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/owners-china-based-company-charged-us-with-conspiracy-steal-secrets-2024-03-19/</link><description>一名中国加拿大居民因涉嫌窃取电动汽车制造商特斯拉的商业机密并密谋将其出售给卧底执法人员而在美国被捕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 21:24:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/owners-china-based-company-charged-us-with-conspiracy-steal-secrets-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国副气候特使表示，中美两国正在推进遏制甲烷排放的工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/us-china-advance-work-curbing-methane-emissions-us-deputy-climate-envoy-says-2024-03-19/</link><description>美国气候变化问题副特使周二表示，中美在甲烷方面的合作正在推进，北京有机会以很少或没有成本的方式削减其庞大煤炭行业的排放量。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 17:59:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/us-china-advance-work-curbing-methane-emissions-us-deputy-climate-envoy-says-2024-03-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>